1. PROMPT - CHAINING Design pattern
Prompt chaining is a technique where we get the response from llm and then refeed to the llm.

-----------         -----------       -----------       -----------      -----------        -----------       
|         |         |         |       |         |       |         |      |         |        |         |
|   in    | ----->  |   llm1  |  ---> |  Gate   | ----> |   llm2  | ---> |  llm3   |  --->  |   out   |
|         |         |         |       | (Human) |       |         |      |         |        |         |
-----------         -----------       -----------       -----------      -----------        -----------

